<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Fitness Tracking App - Home</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="hero-section">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Welcome to <span>Fitness Tracker</span></h1>
            <p>Your personal journey to health and wellness starts here.</p>
            <a asp-area="" asp-controller="User" asp-action="Register" class="btn-primary">Get started</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="features">
            <h2>Why Choose Fitness Tracker?</h2>
            <div class="feature-list">
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h3>Track Progress</h3>
                    <p>Monitor your workouts, body weight, and nutrition with ease.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h3>Personalized Goals</h3>
                    <p>Set your goals and stay motivated with customized plans.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h3>Connect with Trainers</h3>
                    <p>Get expert guidance and insights from certified trainers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cta">
            <h2>Join the Fitness Revolution!</h2>
            <p>Take the first step toward a healthier you. Sign up now and transform your life.</p>
            <a asp-area="" asp-controller="User" asp-action="Register" class="btn-secondary">Join Now</a>
        </section>

        <section class="testimonials">
            <h2>What Our Users Say</h2>
            <div class="testimonial-list">
                <div class="testimonial-item">
                    <p>"Fitness Tracker helped me lose 10kg in 3 months. The tools and guidance are amazing!"</p>
                    <span>- Alex P.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="testimonial-item">
                    <p>"The best app for fitness enthusiasts. The trainer dashboard is a game changer!"</p>
                    <span>- Lisa M.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>